{
  "stem": "10698.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they, they had an, an ad in the paper that a granddaughter is looking for somebody if they knew a Barska Fisher from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, my sister called the newspaper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gave the, the people the telephone number to call my sister.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because this was an open house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a matter of fact, my brother's friends, when it came Purim and Hanukkah, they showered my mom with gifts.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they didn't have such open home that they can always come find a meal, find somebody to talk to, spend some time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was the-- and there, and there, there-- always happy, always songs, always so much, so much happiness in the house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so was with my girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They used to come home with me from school and do homework with me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wipe my nose.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have one here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After all, I got misty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, I don't need-- I think that maybe I need it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All that happiness in the house-- always laughter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And during the time when they closed up the ghetto, my mom used to cook.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, we didn't have a maid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The money was there, but the food was scarce, because the ration cards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But whenever she cooked up a pot of soup, the next-door neighbor was getting a portion, and a flight down, the woman that just had a baby.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's how we lived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly at home-- my mom-- they, they-- I had education at home, but yet--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a teacher to come to the house to teach.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I suppose so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the-- even in the library, they said they are running out on books.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I was a bookworm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- I'll tell you before [NON-ENGLISH]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we were very young, we used to go to camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Summer camps-- I'm sorry, kosher camps, by the way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, God, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most, most likely, because there were only Jewish kids in the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dear God, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm blocking out a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then when we got a little older, we were renting a bungalow in, in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You could go by train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could go by car.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I couldn't tell you how many miles-- kilometers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing-- just, just having a good time and having a lot of pictures taken-- that I have a whole album with pictures from [NON-ENGLISH]--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--but I didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were-- some of them were right here in the United States and some in Israel-- that I didn't survive any pictures.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't come out from the concentration camp with pictures.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All those pictures I have, they were here-- my brother in the United States and my Aunt [NON-ENGLISH] in the United States and also some family in Israel had pictures.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a beautiful place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a whole, it was a whole line of resort places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and we went every year there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had, like, I have beautiful pictures taken.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we just enjoyed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like my brother, that's the youngest from the boys, he used to rent a cart with a horse and put us all in the cart and take us for rides.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He just knew everything how to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he took a lot of pictures also, because he was-- he liked to dibble, to dabble into the photography also.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were several Jewish theaters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- the whole house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, you went either Saturday night if it was, you know, Shabbos was out early, or you went Sunday.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was playing all week.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's why I don't enjoy things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw [NON-ENGLISH], which here, it is-- it's in English, and it's dancing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe I, I was in me that I saw it as a drama.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And to me, all that dancing-- and, and I just-- it doesn't register that, that good with me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I don't remember this way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I was a very young girl that I started to go to the theater.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a matter of fact, I met some actors here in the United States that I was very friendly with--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bozyk.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Reizl Bozyk.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- we were very friendly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Reizl Bozyk used to hold me on, on her lap and play with me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we used to go behind the--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah-- to say hello.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Raizel Bozek and her husband, Max Bozek, they remembered us, my sister and myself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I only had school until 16-- three, when the war-- when-- then June, when I would turn 16, there was vacation time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the-- when the Nazis walked in-- you understand, I don't say Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I, I hate when somebody blames a whole people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I always say the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
